      "n": 1,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "N Akaban bija ſeptin-definitis Dehlieekſch Sa-marijas / un Jeũs rak-ſtija Grahmatas/ un fuhtija tahs uhs Samariju pee Jesreẽles Wirſ-nekeem/ pee teem Wezzajeem un Akaba Wehrmindeereem / ar ſcheem Wahrdeem."
    },
    {
      "n": 2,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Rad tchi Grahmata pee juus nahk/ un jujſa Kunga Deh-li pee juus irr/ ir Ratti un Sir-gi/ ſtipri Pilsfahti un Bruknas pee juus irr/"
    },
    {
      "n": 3,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tad tsredseet to labbaku un taifun no jujſa Kunga Deh-leem / un eezelleet to us winna Tehwa Gohda-Krehflu / un kar-rojeet par juhsa Kunga Namimu."
    },
    {
      "n": 4,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Bet tee bihjajahs warren lohti/ un fazzija: Raugi/ diwi Rehnini ne irr winna Breekſcha pastahwejtchi/ ka tad mehs pa-stahweſim?"
    },
    {
      "n": 5,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tad fuhtija tas/ kas pahr to Nammu btja eezelts/ ir ta Pilsfahta Waldneeks / un tee Wezzajee/ un Wehrmindee pee Jeitu/ un fazzija: Mehs efam tawi Kalpi/ un darrifim wiſſu/ ko tu unmē fazzifi/ mehs ne wee-nu par Rehninu darrifim/ darri tu/ kas tew patihk."
    },
    {
      "n": 6,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tad rakſtija wiſch zittu Grahmatu ar ſcheem Wahrdeem: Ja juhs man peederrat/ un man-nai Balkfnet gribbat klausiht/ nd nemmeet tahs Galwas no"
    },
    {
      "n": 7,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "teem Wiḣreem juhsu Kunga Dehleem/ un nahzeet pee man riht ap ſcho Laiku uhs Jesreẽli. (Un ta Rehnina Dehlu bija ſep-tindeſints Wihrn/ pee ta Pils-tahta Leeleem-Kungcem/ kas tohs usaundſinaja.)"
    },
    {
      "n": 7,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Rad nu ſchi Grahmata pee teem nahze / tad nehine tee ta Rehnina Dehlu/ un nokawe ſeptindeſints Wihrus / un liſſe winnu Galwas eekſch Kurwjeemi/ un fuhtija tohs uhs Jesreẽli."
    },
    {
      "n": 8,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un tad tas Webſnetis nah-ze/ un wiſſam to stahtija/ faz-zidams: Tee irr to Rehnina Deh-liu Galwas atneſſuchi / tad faz-zija wiſch: Leezeet tohs diwe-jās Kohpās / pee to Wahrtu Durwin lihds Rihtam."
    },
    {
      "n": 9,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un Rihta/ kad wiſch iſ-gahje / tad pastahweja wiſch tur/ un fazzija us wiſſeim Lau-dim: Juhs effat taitni/ rangi/ eſmu es weenu Derribu prett mannu Kungu darrifs/ un wiſ-ſu nokawis / kas tad irr ſchohs wiſſus kawis?"
    },
    {
      "n": 10,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tapehz atſibſteet / ka ne neeka no ta KUNGA Wahrdn pee Semnes krittibs / fo tas KUNGS prett Akaba Nammu runnajs / jo tas KUNGS irr darrifs / fo wiſch zaar tayou Kalpu Elijasu rinnajs."
    },
    {
      "n": 11,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tad kawe Jeũs arridsan wiſſus/ kas no Akaba Namma atliſſe eeſſch Jesreẽles/ ir wiſſus winna Angstneeks/ un winna Paſihſtamus/ un winna Sweh-"
    }
  ],
  "confidence": "high",
